msgid "Select one file in each panel and use <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Compare by content...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. &krusader; will open an external graphical difference tool that is <link linkend=\"konfig-dependencies\">configured</link>. &kompare;, <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</application></ulink> and <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/\"><application>xxdiff</application></ulink> are supported."
